  "displayName": "Luciano Mammino",
  "headline": "",
  "summary": "Full-stack developer turned cloud architect, Luciano Mammino is an AWS Serverless Hero, author of Node.js Design Patterns (https://nodejsdesignpatterns.com/), and co-author of the e-book Crafting Lambda Functions in Rust (https://rust-lambda.com/). He is also the original author of Middy (https://middy.js.org/), the Node.js middleware engine for AWS Lambda. At fourTheorem (https://fourtheorem.com/), he helps companies be successful with AWS through pragmatic, scalable serverless architectures. He loves building with JavaScript/TypeScript, Rust, and modern cloud systems.",
